name: NFT Babe <3
description:
It's almost the end of year, some of us are busy prepare our lives, improve and share things with others. So far, we are all helped each other. Sometimes there are people who doesn't know that girls are vibing here. I got called as "dude", "man" and that happened to some girl babes here, it proved that in the end our values is not depends in our genders. we are all so equal and this brand new identity in nft, metaverse, blockchain system are giving us a new power of creation and communication. 

love the way it goes, love the way people were never give up. keep collecting and creating NFTs, cause it won't stop on you, on us, it will work for the future.
